<div data-modal-target="modal"
     data-action="click->modal#backdropClick"
     class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 items-center justify-center z-50 hidden">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-md w-full mx-4 shadow-2xl">
    <div class="mb-6 text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="text-3xl">📜</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">Game Rules</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">🎯 Main Objective</h3>
        <p class="mb-3">Guide your pet to reach the target using Ruby code commands like <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">left</code>, <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">right</code>, <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">up</code>, and <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">down</code>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">🍪 Treats for Bonus Points</h3>
        <p class="mb-3">Collect treats along the way to earn extra points! Each treat adds bonus points to your score.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">🕳️ Watch Out for Holes!</h3>
        <p class="mb-3">Avoid falling into holes! If your pet falls into a hole, you'll lose a life and need to restart the level.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">💡 Tips</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Use loops like <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">5.times { right }</code> to move efficiently</li>
          <li>Plan your path carefully to collect treats and avoid holes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-center">
      <button data-action="click->modal#hide"
              class="bg-blue-500 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors font-medium">
        Got it!
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
